      "content": "i'm honestly losing my mind. spent all day at the office doing soul-crushing data entry but then i saw the new draft for the ASEAN-Pacific trade protocols... i saw my own syntax in the sub-clauses. the exact way i structure contingency frameworks. they really think they can just strip my name from the primary authorship and pretend someone else did the heavy lifting for the 2022 summit. it's like they're trying to erase me from the very history i helped build. do you see how weird that is?",
